title: JRE Review of 1298 with Neal Brennan
description:
Neal is one of the greats and a fantastic joke writer. He is working on a new comedy special and his last one 3 mics was so good that I can't wait to see what he comes out with. He also has a new podcast called How Neal Feels so check that out. He's always a great guest to listen to and then review.

 

Enjoy my review folks!
